---
import {Image} from "astro:assets"
import H2 from "./CustomUI/H2.astro"
import Reel_1 from "/Reel_1.mp4";
import Reel_2 from "/Reel_2.mp4";
import Reel_3 from "/Reel_3.mp4";
import Reel_4 from "/Reel_4.mp4";
---

<section class="max-w-6xl pt-12">
<div class="font-PP grid grid-cols-3">
    <div class="col-span-3 md:col-span-2 w-[90%] flex justify-center flex-col">
    <H2 class="font-PPMedium text-xl py-4">Editing travels</H2>
    <div class="lg:max-w-3xl text-[16px]">
<p>What started as a page to test out video editing features in Adobe Express and competitor apps has become a continued project, <a href="https://instagram.com/twisted.roads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-PPMedium hover: hover:underline transition-colors duration-200 inline-flex items-center gap-0.5">@twisted.roads<svg class="inline-block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg></a><a href="https://instagram.com/bow.craftworks" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-PPMedium hover: hover:underline transition-colors duration-200 inline-flex items-center gap-0.5">@bow.craftworks<svg class="inline-block" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg></a> on instagram, for documenting my travels strictly through mobile edits.</p>
    </div>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="col-span-3 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mt-10 ">
    <video class="rounded-xl" autoplay loop muted playsinline width="100%">
    <source src={Reel_1} type="video/mp4" />
  </video>
  <video class="rounded-xl" autoplay loop muted playsinline width="100%">
    <source src={Reel_2} type="video/mp4" />
  </video>
  <video class="rounded-xl" autoplay loop muted playsinline width="100%">
    <source src={Reel_3} type="video/mp4" />
  </video>
  <video class="rounded-xl" autoplay loop muted playsinline width="100%">
    <source src={Reel_4} type="video/mp4" />
  </video>
    </div>
</div>




</section>
